      <conbody>
        <p>Use the view attribute of the permissions element set in the
DITAMAP metadata to control confidentiality notices.
Confidentiality notices appear in the footer of each page.</p>
    <codeblock id="codeblock_m42_34j_zwb">&lt;bookmap&gt;
    &lt;booktitle&gt;
        &lt;mainbooktitle&gt;Document Title&lt;/mainbooktitle&gt;
    &lt;/booktitle&gt;
    &lt;bookmeta&gt;
        &lt;permissions view="internal"/>
    &lt;/bookmeta&gt;
    &lt;booktitle></codeblock>
        <p>Applicable values are the following:</p>
        <table>
      <title>View attribute</title>
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="2.0*"/>
            <colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="1.0*"/>
            <colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="2.0*"/>
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Target audience</entry>
            <entry>View attribute value</entry>
            <entry>Confidentiality notice</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry>Document is for customers or the general public
<b>and</b> does not have any confidential or proprietary
information</entry>
                <entry><codeph>all</codeph> or unset</entry>
                <entry>N/A</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>Document is for HPE employees <b>and is not</b> to be
shared with customers or partners</entry>
                <entry><codeph>internal</codeph></entry>
                <entry>HPE Internal Use Only</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>Document is for HPE employees <b>and</b> partners who
have agreed to keep it confidential <b>and is not</b> to
be shared with customers</entry>
                <entry><codeph>entitled</codeph></entry>
                <entry>Confidential | Authorized HPE Partner Use Only</entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>Document is for training HPE Employees, Outsourced, Channel
Partners and Customer Education training material</entry>
                <entry><codeph>classified</codeph></entry>
                <entry>Confidential â€“ For Training Purposes Only</entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
      </conbody>
